or primera vez permitió la oficina. despacho. En los años siguientes, también creó un mercado en crecimiento para juegos, aplicaciones y utilidades. DOS, el primer sistema operativo de<br></p>', 'software,computadoras,cada,compa,primera,tica,inform,para,Computer,permitido,Corporation,universidades,mercado,principios,industria', 'P', '2018-09-15 10:35:22', NULL, 92, 8),
(11, 'l\'industrie pétrolière Fr\r\n', 54, 50, 45, 32, '<div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"padding-left: 1.6em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\"><font color=\"#222222\" face=\"sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><i>\"Patch huile\" redirige ici. Pour le magazine, reportez-vous à la rubrique Hotline de correction des huiles.</i></span></font><br></div><div class=\"thumb tright\" style=\"clear: right; float: right; margin: 0.5em 0px 1.3em 1.4em; width: auto; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"min-width: 100px; border: 1px solid rgb(200, 204, 209); padding: 3px; background-color: rgb(248, 249, 250); font-size: 13.16px; text-align: center; overflow: hidden; width: 402px;\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Oil_Reserves.png\" class=\"image\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e3/Oil_Reserves.png/400px-Oil_Reserves.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"182\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e3/Oil_Reserves.png/600px-Oil_Reserves.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e3/Oil_Reserves.png/800px-Oil_Reserves.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"1799\" data-file-height=\"819\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(200, 204, 209); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></a><div class=\"thumbcaption\" style=\"border: 0px; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 3px; font-size: 12.3704px; text-align: left;\"><div class=\"magnify\" style=\"float: right; margin-left: 3px; margin-right: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Oil_Reserves.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: linear-gradient(transparent, transparent), url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22 viewBox=%220 0 11 15%22 width=%2215%22 height=%2211%22%3E %3Cg id=%22magnify-clip%22 fill=%22%23fff%22 stroke=%22%23000%22%3E %3Cpath id=%22bigbox%22 d=%22M1.509 1.865h10.99v7.919h-10.99z%22/%3E %3Cpath id=%22smallbox%22 d=%22M-1.499 6.868h5.943v4.904h-5.943z%22/%3E %3C/g%3E %3C/svg%3E&quot;); background-position-x: initial, initial; background-position-y: initial, initial; background-size: initial, initial; background-repeat: repeat, repeat; background-attachment: initial, initial; background-origin: initial, initial; background-clip: initial, initial; display: block; text-indent: 15px; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; width: 15px; height: 11px; user-select: none;\"></a></div>World&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oil_reserves\" title=\"Oil reserves\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">oil reserves</a>, 2013.</div></div></div><div class=\"thumb tright\" style=\"clear: right; float: right; margin: 0.5em 0px 1.3em 1.4em; width: auto; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"min-width: 100px; border: 1px solid rgb(200, 204, 209); padding: 3px; background-color: rgb(248, 249, 250); font-size: 13.16px; text-align: center; overflow: hidden; width: 402px;\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Reservespie.png\" class=\"image\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/11/Reservespie.png/400px-Reservespie.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"291\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/11/Reservespie.png/600px-Reservespie.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/11/Reservespie.png/800px-Reservespie.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"911\" data-file-height=\"663\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(200, 204, 209); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></a><div class=\"thumbcaption\" style=\"border: 0px; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 3px; font-size: 12.3704px; text-align: left;\"><div class=\"magnify\" style=\"float: right; margin-left: 3px; margin-right: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Reservespie.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: linear-gradient(transparent, transparent), url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22 viewBox=%220 0 11 15%22 width=%2215%22 height=%2211%22%3E %3Cg id=%22magnify-clip%22 fill=%22%23fff%22 stroke=%22%23000%22%3E %3Cpath id=%22bigbox%22 d=%22M1.509 1.865h10.99v7.919h-10.99z%22/%3E %3Cpath id=%22smallbox%22 d=%22M-1.499 6.868h5.943v4.904h-5.943z%22/%3E %3C/g%3E %3C/svg%3E&quot;); background-position-x: initial, initial; background-position-y: initial, initial; background-size: initial, initial; background-repeat: repeat, repeat; background-attachment: initial, initial; background-origin: initial, initial; background-clip: initial, initial; display: block; text-indent: 15px; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; width: 15px; height: 11px; user-select: none;\"></a></div>The distribution of oil and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_countries_by_natural_gas_proven_reserves\" title=\"List of countries by natural gas proven reserves\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">gas reserves</a>&nbsp;among the world\'s 50 largest oil companies. The reserves of the privately owned companies are grouped together. The oil produced by the \"supermajor\" companies accounts for less than 15% of the total world supply. Over 80% of the world\'s reserves of oil and natural gas are controlled by&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/National_oil_company\" title=\"National oil company\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">national oil companies</a>. Of the world\'s 20 largest oil companies, 15 are&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/State-owned_enterprise\" title=\"State-owned enterprise\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">state-owned oil companies</a>.</div></div></div><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">The&nbsp;<b>petroleum industry</b>, also known as the&nbsp;<b>oil industry</b>&nbsp;or the&nbsp;<b>oil patch</b>, includes the global processes of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hydrocarbon_exploration\" title=\"Hydrocarbon exploration\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">exploration</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Extraction_of_petroleum\" title=\"Extraction of petroleum\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">extraction</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oil_refinery\" title=\"Oil refinery\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">refining</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Petroleum_transport\" title=\"Petroleum transport\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">transporting</a>&nbsp;(often by&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oil_tanker\" title=\"Oil tanker\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">oil tankers</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pipeline_transport\" title=\"Pipeline transport\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">pipelines</a>), and marketing of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_crude_oil_products\" title=\"List of crude oil products\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">petroleum products</a>. The largest volume products of the industry are&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fuel_oil\" title=\"Fuel oil\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">fuel oil</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gasoline\" title=\"Gasoline\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">gasoline</a>(petrol). Petroleum (oil) is also the raw material for many&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Petrochemical\" title=\"Petrochemical\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">chemical products</a>, including&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pharmaceutical_drug\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Pharmaceutical drug\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">pharmaceuticals</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Solvent\" title=\"Solvent\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">solvents</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fertilizer\" title=\"Fertilizer\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">fertilizers</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pesticide\" title=\"Pesticide\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">pesticides</a>, synthetic fragrances, and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Plastic\" title=\"Plastic\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">plastics</a>. The extreme monetary value of oil and its products has led to it being known as \"black gold\". The industry is usually divided into three major components:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Upstream_(petroleum_industry)\" title=\"Upstream (petroleum industry)\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">upstream</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Midstream\" title=\"Midstream\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">midstream</a>, and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Downstream_(petroleum_industry)\" title=\"\" style=\"text-decoration-line: underline; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">downstream</a>. Midstream operations are often included in the downstream category.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Petroleum is vital to many industries, and is of importance to the maintenance of industrial&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Civilization\" title=\"Civilization\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">civilization</a>in its current configuration, and thus is </span><font color=\"#222222\" face=\"sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">une préoccupation critique pour de nombreuses nations. Le pétrole représente un pourcentage important de la consommation mondiale d’énergie, allant de 32% pour l’Europe et l’Asie à 53% pour le Moyen-Orient.</span></font></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit;\"><font color=\"#222222\" face=\"sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br></span></font></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit;\"><font color=\"#222222\" face=\"sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Les modes de consommation des autres régions géographiques sont les suivants: Amérique du Sud et centrale (44%), Afrique (41%) et Amérique du Nord (40%). Le monde consomme 30 milliards de barils (4,8 km³) de pétrole par an, les pays développés étant les plus gros consommateurs. Les États-Unis ont consommé 25% de l\'huile produite en 2007. [1] La production, la distribution, le raffinage et la vente au détail du pétrole dans son ensemble représentent la plus grande industrie au monde en termes de valeur monétaire.</span></font></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit;\"><font color=\"#222222\" face=\"sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br></span></font></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit;\"><font color=\"#222222\" face=\"sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Des gouvernements tels que le gouvernement des États-Unis accordent une forte subvention publique aux sociétés pétrolières, avec d\'importants allégements fiscaux à pratiquement tous les stades de l\'exploration et de l\'extraction pétrolières, y compris les coûts des baux des champs pétroliers et du matériel de forage. [2]</span></font></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit;\"><font color=\"#222222\" face=\"sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br></span></font></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit;\"><font color=\"#222222\" face=\"sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Ces dernières années, la fracturation hydraulique est passée au premier plan de l\'industrie, car cette nouvelle technologie joue un rôle extrêmement crucial et controversé dans les nouvelles méthodes d\'extraction du pétrole. [3]</span></font></p>', 'nbsp,companies,products,industry,trole,reserves,pour,largest,world\'s,downstream,many,plus,often,tats-Unis,Petroleum', 'D', '2018-09-15 11:01:21', NULL, 103, 6),
(12, 'industria petrolera Sp', 55, 51, 46, 28, '<div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic; padding-left: 1.6em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">El \"parche de aceite\" redirige aquí. Para la revista, vea Oil Patch Hotline.<br></div><div class=\"thumb tright\" style=\"clear: right; float: right; margin: 0.5em 0px 1.3em 1.4em; width: auto; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"min-width: 100px; border: 1px solid rgb(200, 204, 209); padding: 3px; background-color: rgb(248, 249, 250); font-size: 13.16px; text-align: center; overflow: hidden; width: 402px;\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Oil_Reserves.png\" class=\"image\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e3/Oil_Reserves.png/400px-Oil_Reserves.png\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e3/Oil_Reserves.png/600px-Oil_Reserves.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e3/Oil_Reserves.png/800px-Oil_Reserves.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"1799\" data-file-height=\"819\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(200, 204, 209); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" width=\"400\" height=\"182\"></a><div class=\"thumbcaption\" style=\"border: 0px; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 3px; font-size: 12.3704px; text-align: left;\"><div class=\"magnify\" style=\"float: right; margin-left: 3px; margin-right: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Oil_Reserves.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: linear-gradient(transparent, transparent), url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22 viewBox=%220 0 11 15%22 width=%2215%22 height=%2211%22%3E %3Cg id=%22magnify-clip%22 fill=%22%23fff%22 stroke=%22%23000%22%3E %3Cpath id=%22bigbox%22 d=%22M1.509 1.865h10.99v7.919h-10.99z%22/%3E %3Cpath id=%22smallbox%22 d=%22M-1.499 6.868h5.943v4.904h-5.943z%22/%3E %3C/g%3E %3C/svg%3E&quot;); background-position-x: initial, initial; background-position-y: initial, initial; background-size: initial, initial; background-repeat: repeat, repeat; background-attachment: initial, initial; background-origin: initial, initial; background-clip: initial, initial; display: block; text-indent: 15px; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; width: 15px; height: 11px; user-select: none;\"></a></div>World&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oil_reserves\" title=\"Oil reserves\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">oil reserves</a>, 2013.</div></div></div><div class=\"thumb tright\" style=\"clear: right; float: right; margin: 0.5em 0px 1.3em 1.4em; width: auto; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"min-width: 100px; border: 1px solid rgb(200, 204, 209); padding: 3px; background-color: rgb(248, 249, 250); font-size: 13.16px; text-align: center; overflow: hidden; width: 402px;\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Reservespie.png\" class=\"image\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/11/Reservespie.png/400px-Reservespie.png\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/11/Reservespie.png/600px-Reservespie.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/11/Reservespie.png/800px-Reservespie.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"911\" data-file-height=\"663\" style=\"border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(200, 204, 209); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" width=\"400\" height=\"291\"></a><div class=\"thumbcaption\" style=\"border: 0px; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 3px; font-size: 12.3704px; text-align: left;\"><div class=\"magnify\" style=\"float: right; margin-left: 3px; margin-right: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Reservespie.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: linear-gradient(transparent, transparent), url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22 viewBox=%220 0 11 15%22 width=%2215%22 height=%2211%22%3E %3Cg id=%22magnify-clip%22 fill=%22%23fff%22 stroke=%22%23000%22%3E %3Cpath id=%22bigbox%22 d=%22M1.509 1.865h10.99v7.919h-10.99z%22/%3E %3Cpath id=%22smallbox%22 d=%22M-1.499 6.868h5.943v4.904h-5.943z%22/%3E %3C/g%3E %3C/svg%3E&quot;); background-position-x: initial, initial; background-position-y: initial, initial; background-size: initial, initial; background-repeat: repeat, repeat; background-attachment: initial, initial; background-origin: initial, initial; background-clip: initial, initial; display: block; text-indent: 15px; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; width: 15px; height: 11px; user-select: none;\"></a></div>The distribution of oil and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_countries_by_natural_gas_proven_reserves\" title=\"List of countries by natural gas proven reserves\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">gas reserves</a>&nbsp;among the world\'s 50 largest oil companies. The reserves of the privately owned companies are grouped together. The oil produced by the \"supermajor\" companies accounts for less than 15% of the total world supply. Over 80% of the world\'s reserves of oil and natural gas are controlled by&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/National_oil_company\" title=\"National oil company\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">national oil companies</a>. Of the world\'s 20 largest oil companies, 15 are&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/State-owned_enterprise\" title=\"State-owned enterprise\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">state-owned oil companies</a>.</div></div></div><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">The&nbsp;<b>petroleum industry</b>, also known as the&nbsp;<b>oil industry</b>&nbsp;or the&nbsp;<b>oil patch</b>, includes the global processes de exploración, extracción, refinación, transporte (a menudo en petroleros y ductos) y comercialización de productos petrolíferos. Los productos de mayor volumen de la industria son fuel oil y gasolina (gasolina). El petróleo (petróleo) también es la materia prima para muchos productos químicos, incluidos productos farmacéuticos, solventes, fertilizantes, pesticidas, fragancias sintéticas y plásticos. El valor monetario extremo del petróleo y sus productos ha llevado a que se lo conozca como \"oro negro\". La industria generalmente se divide en tres componentes principales: upstream, midstream y downstream. Las operaciones intermedias a menudo se incluyen en la categoría descendente.<br><br>El petróleo es vital para muchas industrias, y es de importancia para el mantenimiento de la civilización industrial en su configuración actual, y por lo tanto es una preocupación fundamental para muchas naciones. El petróleo representa un gran porcentaje del consumo mundial de energía, desde un mínimo del 32% para Europa y Asia hasta un máximo del 53% para Oriente Medio.<br><br>Los patrones de consumo de otras regiones geográficas son los siguientes: América del Sur y Central (44%), África (41%) y América del Norte (40%). El mundo consume 30 mil millones de barriles (4,8 km³) de petróleo por año, siendo los países desarrollados los mayores consumidores. Estados Unidos consumió el 25% del petróleo producido en 2007. [1] La producción, distribución, refinación y venta al por menor de petróleo tomado en conjunto representa la industria más grande del mundo en términos de valor en dólares.<br><br>Gobiernos como el gobierno de los Estados Unidos otorgan un alto subsidio público a las compañías petroleras, con importantes exenciones impositivas en prácticamente todas las etapas de la exploración y extracción de petróleo, incluidos los costos de los arrendamientos de yacimientos petrolíferos y los equipos de perforación. [2]<br><br>En los últimos años, la fracturación hidráulica se ha movido a la vanguardia de la industria ya que esta nueva tecnología juega un papel extremadamente crucial y controvertido en los nuevos métodos de extracción de petróleo. [3]</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap; font-size: 11.2px;\"></sup></p>', 'petr,nbsp,companies,para,productos,industria,reserves,extracci,world\'s,feros,mundo,industry,refinaci,menudo,exploraci', 'D', '2018-09-15 11:01:51', NULL, 92, 6),
